### Get players by team (URL param - requires %20 for spaces)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/players/team/Athletic%20Club

### Get players by team (Query param - cleaner with spaces)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/players?team=Athletic Club

### Get player by name (Query param - supports partial match)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/players?name=Nico Williams

### Get all forwards with minimum rating 75
GET http://localhost:5000/api/players?position=FWD&minOverall=75

### Get Spanish midfielders
GET http://localhost:5000/api/players?position=MID&nationality=Spain

### Get all players
GET http://localhost:5000/api/players
